# API Bug Reports (Reqres)

## Bug 1

Title: API returns 200 OK for non-existing user

Preconditions:
- API is available

Steps to reproduce:
1. Send GET request to https://reqres.in/api/users/999

Expected result:
- Status code 404 Not Found

Actual result:
- Status code 200 OK

Severity: Medium  
Priority: Medium


## Bug 2

Title: POST request creates user with empty name

Preconditions:
- API is available

Steps to reproduce:
1. Send POST request to https://reqres.in/api/users
2. Body:
{
  "name": "",
  "job": "QA"
}

Expected result:
- Error message should be returned
- User should not be created

Actual result:
- User is created successfully

Severity: High  
Priority: High


## Bug 3

Title: API accepts invalid data types in request body

Preconditions:
- API is available

Steps to reproduce:
1. Send POST request to https://reqres.in/api/users
2. Body:
{
  "name": 12345,
  "job": true
}

Expected result:
- Validation error should be returned

Actual result:
- User is created successfully

Severity: High  
Priority: Medium
